Name:         Blue Whale
Scientific:   Balaenoptera musculus
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Ocean
Diet:         Carnivore (krill)
Lifespan:     80 years
Weight:       150000 kg
Status:       Endangered
Fact:         Largest animal ever known; heart is size of a small car

Name:         Snow Leopard
Scientific:   Panthera uncia
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Mountain
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     15 years
Weight:       55 kg
Status:       Vulnerable
Fact:         Cannot roar; uses long tail as blanket; leaps 15 meters

Name:         Emperor Penguin
Scientific:   Aptenodytes forsteri
Class:        Aves
Habitat:      Antarctic
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     25 years
Weight:       45 kg
Status:       Near Threatened
